{"tid":1042942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国又現特色婚鬧  新娘獻身與公公「下體撞下體」","createTime":"2019-03-02T01:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T06:19:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc65d07d053fbe0fa34387f9da28ba3b64b06ab","tid":1042942,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"低俗婚鬧似乎已成了中國結婚習俗的「主流」，近日再度有網友轉貼低俗婚鬧的現場影片。這次是一名新娘，當著所有親友的面為公公「獻身」，大玩「下體撞下體」。<br />\n<br />\n影片可見雖然新娘與公公都穿著衣服，但下體綁著鐵器，媳婦的下體綁著一個鍋蓋，公公的下體則是綁著一根長約30公分鍋鏟。隨後在眾親友的指導下，公公與新娘開始「下體撞下體」，在鍋鏟撞擊鍋蓋之際，會發出「鏘」的聲響，這時公公要喊「響不響啊」，新娘則回答「響」。但大家都知道，這一句話極富性暗示，「響不響」就是「想不想」的諧音。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190302/640_812f69d509ed50705369166e5f110586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190302%2F640_812f69d509ed50705369166e5f110586.jpg&h=d817afe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190302/1526042/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190302%2F1526042%2F&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7Cxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=7daa0272\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190302%2F1526042%2F&h=5732fea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190302/1526042/</a>"},{"pid":"b4f7e598f4c51d97026f3b745c6f11cee4207800","tid":1042942,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"搞新抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e039061d395a4076cc17cae8958d57be6ee79cc4","tid":1042942,"uid":94480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"肉嫁"},{"pid":"b6c3ab166286ffa3e171ea2f8b13d226609d7122","tid":1042942,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re